08.jpg"></div><span style="color:rgb(60,62,64);font-family:Tahoma, Dotum, '돋움', sans-serif;"></span><div style="text-align:center;" align="center"><p class="" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="center"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">On the 5th, Yuhan University (CEO Hyunjoong
