defined in an agreed-upon way of working, stakeholders are provided with
appropriate guidance to help minimize risk and create a more efficient and
continuous improvement structured framework.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Many companies address sustainability and
integrate into practice &nbsp;ISO provides a
guide to give you the clarity you need for conversation. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">The world has already crossed a series of
tipping points. Over the past decades, it has been defined as a distinct
climate impact, accelerating biodiversity loss rates, plastic waste in the
ocean, land agglomeration and political instability. A new era awaits all of
us. But before the future is too late, we must be aware of the impact of
choices and actions that we will constantly face. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">In 2015, the United Nations set a global agenda
for 2030 around the 1730 Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) to address some
of the most pressing issues on the planet. This established a holistic purpose
aimed at the future of peace and prosperity in the world. It listens to the
urgent call for participation in a global partnership on sustainability that
goes beyond our usual goals and is the key to unlocking our future.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">According to the World Nature Fund (WWF), SDGs
are now becoming a universal language in which governments, non-governmental
organizations and businesses can collaborate around shared sustainability
goals, commitments, achievements and impacts. It also emphasizes the
responsibility of the private sector to address the social and environmental
challenges of each supply chain, integrate sustainability into its core
business mission, and participate in change in the wider sectors in which they
belong.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">WWF points out how sustainability standards can
help accelerate SDG achievement. Sustainability standards are at the heart of
market transformation. It sets standards that address sustainability challenges
and provide ready-made tools to organizations around the world. Incorporating a
variety of key players as standards implements a multi-stakeholder approach
that is critical to the 2030 global agenda.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">McKinsey said that of the 2,900 executives
surveyed from a business perspective, 43% said they align sustainability with
their overall business goals, mission, or values. Management has reduced waste
to 63%, energy use in operations to 64% and corporate reputation for
sustainability at 59%. This shows that sustainability is at the forefront of
today's corporate agenda.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">What the world needs now<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">International standards are the primary tool
for solving the world's many pressing challenges. Composed of standards and
sustainability experts, ISO Guide 82, Guidance for Addressing the
Sustainability of Standards, provides standards developers with guidance on how
to consider sustainability in their creation, revision, and update. It also
raises awareness of sustainability issues among standards authors and provides
a systematic and consistent approach to identifying and evaluating the
sustainability factors essential in any standards decision process.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.375in;" align="center"><img src="http://igcert.cafe24.com/data/editor/2005/9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590657186_9729.jpg" title="9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590657186_9729.jpg"></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.375in;" align="center"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Young
people cultivate gardening on the roof of the city</span></p><p class="" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.375in;" align="justify"><span style="color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">This
guide has recently been updated to contain information on how standards can
support SDG and to maintain standards that will help the world achieve a
sustainable future. Jimmy Yoler, director of the working group that revised the
guide, said that the 2030 SDG is the main task of revising the guide so that
the sustainability expressed through the SDG is expressed through the SDG and
included in the standard. “ISO Guide 82 enhances our understanding of what
sustainability is and emphasizes a multifaceted approach to dealing with it in
standards making. This guide is a valuable asset for standard developers to
deliver the 2030 Global Agenda.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">There
is also zero guidance on how sustainable development should be considered
during the formation of the committee and in subsequent stages of the standards
development process. This includes SDGs that the committee's work can support.
Rather than raising awareness of sustainable development among the committee's
leadership and participants, it provides guidance on how sustainable development
can be incorporated into the technical committee's scope, structure and
strategic plan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Sustainable
Solutions for Everyone<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">The
SDGs set ambitious targets in 2030 and national development priorities must
align with that vision, but joint efforts are needed to make that vision a
reality. Creating standards can be a complex process that requires adapting to
an ever-changing environment and environment, taking into account the three
pillars of sustainable development of society, economy and the environment.
Sustainability as a whole is much more likely to be achieved if these three
aspects are dealt with in a truly equal and cohesive manner. Actions to address
issues in these areas affect each other. Understanding dynamic interdependence
is critical to driving a sustainable solution that includes all three pillars.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">It
can be said that there are similarities in addressing the sustainability of the
standard and addressing the sustainability issues of an organization. If
multiple sustainability issues are identified as relevant and important, there
may be multiple solutions to address them. In these cases, conflicts can occur.
In other words, implementing a solution to one problem may not implement a
solution to another problem or may deepen the impact of another problem.
Standard developers should be aware that there may be several suitable ways to
solve these problems, and the resources and capabilities required to implement
a particular solution can vary considerably.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">In
these cases, Yoler says, the standard developer should adjust the conflict
whenever possible. Alternatively, you could consider offering multiple options
so that standard users can recognize their concerns and decide which one to
adopt. “ISO Guide 82 urges standards developers to respect, consider and
respond to the needs of relevant stakeholders and, where possible and
practical, encourages participation in the sharing of ideas and information
based on broad and balanced expertise and expression-based opinions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.375in;" align="justify"><br></p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">&nbsp;<img src="http://igcert.cafe24.com/data/editor/2005/9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590657252_7236.jpg" title="9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590657252_7236.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Making
sustainability a reality<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">As
sustainable development and progress towards sustainability is highly dependent
on a number of factors, ISO Guide 82 describes a methodology that standards
developers can use to develop their own approaches to addressing thematic
sustainability. For reference, ISO/TC 17/SC 16, ISO's technical subcommittee
responsible for the standardization of quality, dimensions and tolerances and
other related properties suitable for steel for reinforcement of concrete and
prestressed steels is in progress.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Jan
Karlsen, chairman of this subcommittee, stated that ISO Guide 82 is an
important document in future work. In 2019, several action plans were
determined that would bring the sustainability of work under the SDGs, and assessments
were conducted to determine which plans are critical to achieving specific
goals. “ISO Guide 82 was one of the key documents used as a tool for its
assessment, and committee members found it a practical and useful tool for
developing and sustainable standards.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">The
subcommittee's recent agreement concluded with the establishment of a broad
group of sustainability experts to protect sustainability to be considered in
the standard decision process. “As recommended in ISO Guide 82, we are
committed to recognizing the important role that sustainability professionals
play in this regard and to guide them in the right direction,” adds Karlsen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">The
impact of sustainability standards has increased in recent years. By
facilitating dialogue between multiple stakeholders across a sector, the entire
system can be impacted in countless ways. This not only allows us to improve
strategies and partnerships to address key sustainability issues, but it also
builds mutual trust and empowers those who are often excluded from decisions
that influence or affect attitudes. The standards considered the basis of
sustainability are designed to address the most pressing social and
environmental problems of our time. At the same time, standards are constantly
evolving in a constant struggle for legitimacy and real impact on the earth.
What these developments represent is recognizing the complexity of
sustainability issues facing the beginning of standards, and standardization
plays an important role in transforming the world into a sustainable world.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" align="justify" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">Including
sustainability issues in the creation of the standard itself means that its
core is being addressed. With sustainability at the forefront of the 2030
Global Agenda, standards authors around the world are encouraged to take this
into account at all stages of the standards development process. This will help
protect against the impact of the most important sustainability issues
worldwide. Accordingly, ISO Guide 82 hopes that standards can add value to
society by enabling them to build a better future for all of us.<o:p></o:p></span></p><div style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="color: rgb(0, 117, 200); font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></div>";s:12:"wr_seo_title";s:63:"sustainable-future-formation-sustainable-development-goals-sdgs";s:8:"wr_link1";s:0:"";s:8:"wr_link2";s:0:"";s:12:"wr_link1_hit";s:1:"0";s:12:"wr_link2_hit";s:1:"0";s:6:"wr_hit";s:3:"635";s:7:"wr_good";s:1:"0";s:9:"wr_nogood";s:1:"0";s:5:"mb_id";s:5:"admin";s:7:"wr_name";s:12:"igc인증원";s:8:"wr_email";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_homepage";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_datetime";s:19:"2020-05-28 18:11:25";s:7:"wr_file";s:1:"0";s:7:"wr_last";s:19:"2020-05-28 18:11:25";s:5:"wr_ip";s:12:"61.75.28.173";s:16:"wr_facebook_user";s:0:"";s:15:"wr_twitter_user";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_1";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_2";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_3";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_4";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_5";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_6";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_7";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_8";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_9";s:0:"";s:5:"wr_10";s:0:"";s:9:"is_notice";b:0;s:7:"subject";s:27:"Sustainable Future Forma…";s:11:"comment_cnt";s:0:"";s:8:"datetime";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:9:"datetime2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"last";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:5:"last2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"name";s:43:"<span class="sv_member">igc인증원</span>";s:5:"reply";i:0;s:10:"icon_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"icon_link";s:0:"";s:12:"ca_name_href";s:81:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;sca=";s:4:"href";s:85:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=11";s:12:"comment_href";s:85:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=11";s:8:"icon_new";s:0:"";s:8:"icon_hot";s:0:"";s:11:"icon_secret";s:0:"";s:4:"link";a:2:{i:1;N;i:2;N;}s:9:"link_href";a:2:{i:1;s:93:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=11&amp;no=1";i:2;s:93:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=11&amp;no=2";}s:8:"link_hit";a:2:{i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;}s:4:"file";a:1:{s:5:"count";s:1:"0";}s:16:"first_file_thumb";a:2:{s:7:"bf_file";s:0:"";s:10:"bf_content";s:0:"";}s:8:"bo_table";s:7:"free_en";}i:3;a:62:{s:5:"wr_id";s:2:"10";s:6:"wr_num";s:3:"-10";s:8:"wr_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_parent";s:2:"10";s:13:"wr_is_comment";s:1:"0";s:10:"wr_comment";s:1:"0";s:16:"wr_comment_reply";s:0:"";s:7:"ca_name";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_option";s:5:"html1";s:10:"wr_subject";s:43:"세계 계측의 날,  ISO 무역에 적합";s:10:"wr_content";s:15840:"<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in; font-family: inherit; font-size: 54pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt;">세계 계측의 날 무역에 적합</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 7pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 20.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">조화 된 측정은 관련된 모든 사람이
동일한 언어를 사용하고 공정한 거래를</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">하고 있음을 알 수 있기
때문에 측정은 전 세계 무역의 핵심 요소입니다.&nbsp;그렇기 때문에 올해 세계 도량법의 날을 주제로</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">하며 많은 ISO 표준이 작동에 중요한 역할을</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 20.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 20.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">세계 계측의 날 2020의 주제는
공정한 세계 무역에서 측정의 중요성과 과학적 발견, 혁신, 신제품 개발, 제조 및 지속 가능성에서 중요한 역할을 강조하기</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">위한</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">“세계 무역 측정”입니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">조화 롭고 국제적으로 합의된
방식으로 사물을 측정하는 방법은 우리 사회의 근간이</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">되므로 과학자, 학계, 기업
및 정부가 사용하는 국제 단위 시스템 (SI)에 정의되어 있습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">운송 포장 및 컨테이너 선박에서
제품 자체의 크기에 이르기까지 조화된 수량과 단위가 거래 프로세스의 여러 측면에서 사용된다는 것을 감안할 때</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>SI는 문자 그대로</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">“세계를 돌아 다니게”합니다.&nbsp;국제적으로 합의된 측정 방법은 적합성 평가를 지원하여 효율적인
물류뿐만 아니라 법적 요구 사항과 고객 기대도를 만족시킵니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">ISO 및
IEC&nbsp;(International Electrotechnical Commission)에서 각각 발행&nbsp;한 ISO 및 IEC
80000 표준,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">수량 및 단위</span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">&nbsp;는 국제
시스템이 통일된 용어, 정의 및 기호의 조화된 용어를 제공하므로 SI의 핵심 구성 요소입니다. 단위는 기반입니다.&nbsp;이 표준은 과학자,
엔지니어 및 측정 분야에 관련된 다른 사람</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">간에 정확한 측정 정보를
전달할 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있는 통합 언어를 제공합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">표준을 개발하는 ISO 기술위원회의 의장 인 Leslie Pendrill
교수&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">[&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/news/ref2513.html#note1"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;]</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;는 ISO / IEC 80000 시리즈가 과학자, 엔지니어, 생산자, 소비자 및 제 3 자
사이에서 정확하고 일관된 측정 정보의 통신을 보장한다고 말했다. </span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">“표준화되지 않은 수량과 단위를
사용하는 것은 거래에</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있어 심각한 장벽입니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">“제품의 수량, 품질, 안전성,
견고성 및 기타 특성을 결정할 때 측정 및 테스트에 차이가</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있는 경우 판매자와 구매자가
상품의 가치를 다르게 추정 할 수 있습니다.&nbsp;측정 불확실성과 도량형 추적 성은 판매자와 구매자에 의해 다르게 추정 될 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있어, 거래를 복잡하거나 심지어 불가능하게 만들 수 있습니다.”</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">세계 무역 측정의 기본이</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">되는 다른 표준은</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">화물 컨테이너에 대한
표준입니다.&nbsp;컨테이너화는 운송 인프라의 세계에 혁명을 일으켰으며 현재 비 벌크 제품의 90 %가 복합 컨테이너로 이동하고
있습니다.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">ISO는 컨테이너의 전체 크기에서 쌓을 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있는 방법에 이르기까지 거의 모든 측면을 표준화하여 전세계 어디에서나 사용할 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">있어 효율적이고 비용 효율적인 국제 공급망에 기여합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">이 표준을 담당하는 ISO 기술위원회 – ISO / TC
104&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 1, 24);">[&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/news/ref2513.html#note2"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;]</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Freight 컨테이너</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;는 컨테이너 관련 운송 프로젝트 및 활동에 대한 전 세계적으로 합의 된 기준을 구성하는 초기부터 거의
40 가지 표준을 개발했습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">이러한 표준은 국제 노동기구 (ILO), 국제 해사기구 (IMO), 세계 관세기구
(WCO) 및 유럽 연합 경제위원회 (UNECE)를 비롯한 여러 국가 및 지역 정부 기관에서 국제적으로 인정합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">또한 ISO는 측정 조화에 기여하고 의류 및
신발 크기에서 제약, 기하학적 제품 사양 (GPS) 등에 이르기까지 다양한 분야에서 국제 무역을 촉진하는 데 도움이</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">되는 많은 다른 표준을 보유하고
있습니다.&nbsp;국가&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/members.html"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">ISO 회원</span></a><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">&nbsp;&nbsp;또는&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/store.html"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">ISO Store를</span></a><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">&nbsp;통해&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/store.html"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">구입할 수</span></a><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12pt;" lang="ko">&nbsp;있습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.375in; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">1)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
color:#333333">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">ISO
80000 시리즈는 기술위원회&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/committee/46202.html"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">ISO / TC 12</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">수량 및 단위에</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;의해 개발되었으며&nbsp;&nbsp;, 사무국은&nbsp;스웨덴의 ISO 회원 인&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/member/2101.html"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">SIS</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;가 보유하고&nbsp;&nbsp;있습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">2)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
color:#333333">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">사무국&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/committee/51156.html"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">ISO
/ TC 104</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">화물 컨테이너는</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;,에 의해 유지되는&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/member/2188.html"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">ANSI</span></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;상기 USA ISO 용의 부재.</span></p><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>";s:12:"wr_seo_title";s:41:"세계-계측의-날-iso-무역에-적합";s:8:"wr_link1";s:0:"";s:8:"wr_link2";s:0:"";s:12:"wr_link1_hit";s:1:"0";s:12:"wr_link2_hit";s:1:"0";s:6:"wr_hit";s:3:"551";s:7:"wr_good";s:1:"0";s:9:"wr_nogood";s:1:"0";s:5:"mb_id";s:5:"admin";s:7:"wr_name";s:12:"igc인증원";s:8:"wr_email";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_homepage";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_datetime";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:58:45";s:7:"wr_file";s:1:"0";s:7:"wr_last";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:58:45";s:5:"wr_ip";s:12:"61.75.28.173";s:16:"wr_facebook_user";s:0:"";s:15:"wr_twitter_user";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_1";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_2";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_3";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_4";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_5";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_6";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_7";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_8";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_9";s:0:"";s:5:"wr_10";s:0:"";s:9:"is_notice";b:0;s:7:"subject";s:43:"세계 계측의 날,  ISO 무역에 적합";s:11:"comment_cnt";s:0:"";s:8:"datetime";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:9:"datetime2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"last";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:5:"last2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"name";s:43:"<span class="sv_member">igc인증원</span>";s:5:"reply";i:0;s:10:"icon_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"icon_link";s:0:"";s:12:"ca_name_href";s:81:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;sca=";s:4:"href";s:85:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=10";s:12:"comment_href";s:85:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=10";s:8:"icon_new";s:0:"";s:8:"icon_hot";s:0:"";s:11:"icon_secret";s:0:"";s:4:"link";a:2:{i:1;N;i:2;N;}s:9:"link_href";a:2:{i:1;s:93:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=10&amp;no=1";i:2;s:93:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=10&amp;no=2";}s:8:"link_hit";a:2:{i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;}s:4:"file";a:1:{s:5:"count";s:1:"0";}s:16:"first_file_thumb";a:2:{s:7:"bf_file";s:0:"";s:10:"bf_content";s:0:"";}s:8:"bo_table";s:7:"free_en";}i:4;a:62:{s:5:"wr_id";s:1:"9";s:6:"wr_num";s:2:"-9";s:8:"wr_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_parent";s:1:"9";s:13:"wr_is_comment";s:1:"0";s:10:"wr_comment";s:1:"0";s:16:"wr_comment_reply";s:0:"";s:7:"ca_name";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_option";s:5:"html1";s:10:"wr_subject";s:34:"ISO 연구 및 혁신 네트워크";s:10:"wr_content";s:1134:"<p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">ISO 연구 및 혁신 네트워크</span>&nbsp;</b></p><p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><br></b></p><p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><span lang="ko" style="font-size: 12pt;">이</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"> </span><span lang="ko" style="font-size: 12pt;">네트워크는 표준화와 관련된 연구 및 혁신
활동을 논의, 홍보 및 수행하기위한 커뮤니티를 만들기 위해 ISO 연구 및 혁신 (R &amp; I) 부서에서 만들었습니다.</span></b>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><span lang="ko" style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></b></p><div style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><span lang="ko" style="font-size: 12pt;"><img src="http://igcert.cafe24.com/data/editor/2005/9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590656000_2212.jpg" title="9bf08880aadfd60dc5245be72f1ef110_1590656000_2212.jpg"></span></b></div><b><div style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><b><span lang="ko" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></b></div></b>";s:12:"wr_seo_title";s:34:"iso-연구-및-혁신-네트워크";s:8:"wr_link1";s:0:"";s:8:"wr_link2";s:0:"";s:12:"wr_link1_hit";s:1:"0";s:12:"wr_link2_hit";s:1:"0";s:6:"wr_hit";s:3:"513";s:7:"wr_good";s:1:"0";s:9:"wr_nogood";s:1:"0";s:5:"mb_id";s:5:"admin";s:7:"wr_name";s:12:"igc인증원";s:8:"wr_email";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_homepage";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_datetime";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:53:23";s:7:"wr_file";s:1:"0";s:7:"wr_last";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:53:23";s:5:"wr_ip";s:12:"61.75.28.173";s:16:"wr_facebook_user";s:0:"";s:15:"wr_twitter_user";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_1";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_2";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_3";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_4";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_5";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_6";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_7";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_8";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_9";s:0:"";s:5:"wr_10";s:0:"";s:9:"is_notice";b:0;s:7:"subject";s:34:"ISO 연구 및 혁신 네트워크";s:11:"comment_cnt";s:0:"";s:8:"datetime";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:9:"datetime2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"last";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:5:"last2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"name";s:43:"<span class="sv_member">igc인증원</span>";s:5:"reply";i:0;s:10:"icon_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"icon_link";s:0:"";s:12:"ca_name_href";s:81:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;sca=";s:4:"href";s:84:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=9";s:12:"comment_href";s:84:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=9";s:8:"icon_new";s:0:"";s:8:"icon_hot";s:0:"";s:11:"icon_secret";s:0:"";s:4:"link";a:2:{i:1;N;i:2;N;}s:9:"link_href";a:2:{i:1;s:92:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=9&amp;no=1";i:2;s:92:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=9&amp;no=2";}s:8:"link_hit";a:2:{i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;}s:4:"file";a:1:{s:5:"count";s:1:"0";}s:16:"first_file_thumb";a:2:{s:7:"bf_file";s:0:"";s:10:"bf_content";s:0:"";}s:8:"bo_table";s:7:"free_en";}i:5;a:62:{s:5:"wr_id";s:1:"8";s:6:"wr_num";s:2:"-8";s:8:"wr_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_parent";s:1:"8";s:13:"wr_is_comment";s:1:"0";s:10:"wr_comment";s:1:"0";s:16:"wr_comment_reply";s:0:"";s:7:"ca_name";s:0:"";s:9:"wr_option";s:5:"html1";s:10:"wr_subject";s:56:"세상이 멈추어도 표준 개발은 계속됩니다.";s:10:"wr_content";s:15847:"<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in; font-size: 28pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 11pt;">세상이 멈추어도 표준 개발은 계속 움직입니다</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;">.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 20.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">전 세계 어딘가에서 약 5 천 회의가 개최되어 ISO 국제 표준을 개발하여 지구의 4 개 구석에서 온
전문가들을 모았습니다.&nbsp;COVID-19가 여행을 정체 시키자 표준 세계는 문자 그대로 밤새 완전히 온라인
상태가되었습니다.&nbsp;결과 : 더 많은 전문 지식, 더 많은 목소리 및 궁극적으로 더 나은 표준.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 20.25pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">인공 지능에서
아연 합금에 이르기까지 ISO에는&nbsp;전세계 거의 모든 국가의 수십만 명의 전문가들로 구성된&nbsp;300 개 이상의&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/technical-committees.html"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">기술위원회</span></a><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">&nbsp;가 있습니다.&nbsp;이들은 함께 23
000 개가 넘는 ISO 국제 표준을 책임지고 있으며, 더 많은 개발이 이루어지고 있습니다.&nbsp;그러나 3 월에 전염병이 발표되었을 때
ISO위원회는 작업 방식을 빠르게 변경해야</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">했습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">“온라인에서 너무 긴 회의는 누구에게나
효과가 없습니다.&nbsp;따라서 우리는</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">보다 효율적이고</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">보다 타깃화되고 능률적인 방법을 찾았으며 그 결과 상당한 긍정적인 진전이 있었고 많은 영역에서
합의가 이루어졌습니다.”</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">1 주일 내내 하루 종일 대면하는 행사는 2
명의 온라인 미팅으로 바뀌었으며, 2 명의 회원을 포함하여 28 명의 국가에서 온 220 명의 참가자 (한 명의 새로운 회원 포함)가 2
시간에 걸쳐 진행되었습니다.&nbsp;빅 데이터와 AI 내에서 주제가 많은 영역이 논의되었으며 많은 프로젝트가
진행되었습니다.&nbsp;Diab에 따르면 모든 것이 예상보다 낫습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">"훌륭한 팀 정신, 공유 목표 및
결과가 분명했습니다."</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">이 회의는 2020 년 3 월 중순부터
2020 년 8 월 말까지 ISO위원회를 위해 개최된 2 천 건 이상의 직접 회의 중 하나였으며,</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">이 모든 회의는 전염병이 닥쳤을 때
온라인으로 빠르게 이동했습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">AI위원회에게 이것은 모든 준비를</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">하고 모든 사람이 탑승하는 데 몇 주 밖에
걸리지 않았습니다.&nbsp;또한 여러 실무 그룹과 시간대의 요구와 주제를 고려하고 겹침이 없는지 확인하여 의제를 대폭
변경했습니다.&nbsp;새로운 회의 계획을 통해 참가자들은 상황이 모든 사람에게 스트레스가</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">된다는 것을 알고 다른 작업을 처리 할 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">있는 유연성이 필요했습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">회의는 데이터 측면, 사용 사례, 응용
프로그램, 신뢰성, 전산 기법, 거버넌스 영향, AI 지능형 시스템 엔지니어링 등과 같이 AI와 관련하여 우리 모두에게 영향을 미치는 중요한
영역에서 국제 지침 문서 및 표준 개발을 진행하기 위해 개최되었습니다. .</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro;" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">요헨 Fornather, 강화 플라스틱
파이프 및 피팅에 대한 ISO의 소위원회 관리자&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">[&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/news/ref2514.html#note2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background: white;">2</span></a><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">&nbsp;]</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">&nbsp;, 최근의 온라인 미팅은 더 큰 참여와 고체 참여를 유치, 똑같이 성공했다 고 말했다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">그는“유리 섬유 강화 플라스틱 배관 시스템
분야의 기존 표준을 개정 할뿐만 아니라 새로운 표준 및 기술 사양을 연구 중이므로 많은 논의가 필요했다”고 말했다.&nbsp;“의제가
강화되었고 사전에 많은 준비가 완료되었으며 그 결과 평소보다 많은 사람들이 참석했으며 모든 목표를 달성했습니다.&nbsp;우리는 현재 유행성
이상으로</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">이 접근법을 확실히 고려할 것입니다.”</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">이 기간 동안 온라인에서 개최 된 500여 개의
다른 ISO 회의에서 얻은 피드백도 마찬가지로 긍정적으로, 표준 커뮤니티가 모든 곳에서 표준에 대한 토론, 토론 및 개발을 성공적으로 계속하고
있음을 의미합니다.&nbsp;이러한 회의가 사실상 얼마나 오래 지속 될지 또는 유행 후 세계가 어떻게 될지는 확실하지 않지만 ISO 가족은
표준이 항상 이행 될 것임을 입증했습니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">Diab는“AI는 뜨거운 주제이며 우리의 업무
프로그램은 규모와 성장에 따라 200 명 이상의 대표자와 가상 형식으로 효과적이고 효율적인 회의를 운영하는 것이 결코 위업이 아니라는 것을
반영합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">“그러나 전문가들의 따뜻한 커뮤니티, 훌륭한
복원력 및 참여가 표시되었습니다.&nbsp;게다가 3 살짜리 소년이 갑자기 방에 들어선 당황스러운 순간도 없었습니다.”라고 그는 덧붙였다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">"우리는 세상이 곧 정상으로 돌아
오기를 희망하지만 사실상 회의는 확실히 미래에 사용할 수</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">있는 형식입니다."</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-size: 13.5pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" align="justify"><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">ISO는
필요한 경우 전체 프로세스를 원격으로 수행 할 수 있도록 가상 표준 개발 플랫폼을 시험하고 있습니다.&nbsp;2021 년 언젠가는</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">이 옵션을</span><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="en-US"> </span><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: MetaWebPro; background: white; font-size: 11pt;" lang="ko">보다
광범위한 옵션으로 출시 할 계획입니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 11pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 11.45pt;" align="justify"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">1)&nbsp;인공 지능에 대한 ISO의
기술위원회는&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/committee/6794475.html"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">ISO / IEC JTC 1 / SC 42</span></a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;이며, 사무국은&nbsp;미국의 ISO 회원 인&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/member/2188.html"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">ANSI</span></a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;가 보유하고&nbsp;있습니다.&nbsp;ISO와 IEC
(International Electrotechnical Commission)가 공동으로 관리합니다.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 9pt; font-family: MetaWebPro; font-size: 11.45pt;" align="justify"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">2)&nbsp;ISO / TC
138,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">유체
수송 용 플라스틱 파이프, 피팅 및 밸브</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/committee/52590.html"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">SC
6</span></a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">모든 응용 분야를위한 강화 플라스틱
파이프 및 피팅</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;,
사무국은&nbsp;오스트리아의 ISO 회원 인&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.iso.org/member/1529.html"><span style="background: white; font-size: 11pt;">ASI</span></a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;가 보유하고&nbsp;있습니다.</span></p><div style="text-align: justify;" align="justify">&nbsp;</div>";s:12:"wr_seo_title";s:55:"세상이-멈추어도-표준-개발은-계속됩니다";s:8:"wr_link1";s:0:"";s:8:"wr_link2";s:0:"";s:12:"wr_link1_hit";s:1:"0";s:12:"wr_link2_hit";s:1:"0";s:6:"wr_hit";s:3:"518";s:7:"wr_good";s:1:"0";s:9:"wr_nogood";s:1:"0";s:5:"mb_id";s:5:"admin";s:7:"wr_name";s:12:"igc인증원";s:8:"wr_email";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_homepage";s:0:"";s:11:"wr_datetime";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:49:21";s:7:"wr_file";s:1:"0";s:7:"wr_last";s:19:"2020-05-28 17:49:21";s:5:"wr_ip";s:12:"61.75.28.173";s:16:"wr_facebook_user";s:0:"";s:15:"wr_twitter_user";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_1";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_2";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_3";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_4";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_5";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_6";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_7";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_8";s:0:"";s:4:"wr_9";s:0:"";s:5:"wr_10";s:0:"";s:9:"is_notice";b:0;s:7:"subject";s:56:"세상이 멈추어도 표준 개발은 계속됩니다.";s:11:"comment_cnt";s:0:"";s:8:"datetime";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:9:"datetime2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"last";s:10:"2020-05-28";s:5:"last2";s:5:"05-28";s:4:"name";s:43:"<span class="sv_member">igc인증원</span>";s:5:"reply";i:0;s:10:"icon_reply";s:0:"";s:9:"icon_link";s:0:"";s:12:"ca_name_href";s:81:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;sca=";s:4:"href";s:84:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=8";s:12:"comment_href";s:84:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/board.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=8";s:8:"icon_new";s:0:"";s:8:"icon_hot";s:0:"";s:11:"icon_secret";s:0:"";s:4:"link";a:2:{i:1;N;i:2;N;}s:9:"link_href";a:2:{i:1;s:92:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=8&amp;no=1";i:2;s:92:"https://beautycet.mycafe24.com/gpcqua_eng/bbs/link.php?bo_table=free_en&amp;wr_id=8&amp;no=2";}s